Incident 2662-13:  On ██/██/2005, a religious group known as  successfully broke into SCP-2662's containment.

IncidentExcerpt

CredentialsM██




  SCP-2662 is seen eating breakfast and reading a newspaper.

  Security officers stationed at SCP-2662's containment unit enter with a researcher. The researcher can be seen carrying a piglet.



 Researcher ████ proceeds to castrate the piglet in front of SCP-2662 and place the testes on SCP-2662's food.

 Task Force Tau-9 is notified of a breach into containment.

  SCP-2662 attempts to read its newspaper. Researcher ████ slits the piglet's neck and throws it onto the table. Blood splatters the newspaper.

 SCP-2662 puts the newspaper down. The accompanying security officers execute Researcher ████ via gunshot to the head. They then begin consuming her.

  SCP-2662 leaves the scene to vomit in a toilet.

  Task Force Tau-9 arrive to move SCP-2662 to a temporary containment unit and detain the guards.
附加记录：    

After further investigation, all involved personnel were civilians posing as personnel. It is unknown as to the whereabouts of the actual researcher and security officers.




Incident 2662-78:  On ██/██/2014, an unnamed religious group, consisting of D-class personnel and 2 members of Task Force Tau-9, successfully broke into SCP-2662's containment. SCP-2662 was redesignated as Keter upon further review of Incident 2662-78.

IncidentExcerpt

CredentialsM██




  SCP-2662 can be seen sleeping in its bed.

  The entirety of Task Force Tau-9 is called for an off-site mission. Against orders, Task Force Tau-9 chooses to leave 4 of its members behind to keep watch on SCP-2662.

  2 of the remaining members tackle and lock the other 2 in an unused containment unit.

  A cargo truck arrives on Site ██ where SCP-2662 is being kept.

  The 2 remaining members unload the cargo of D-class personnel. They lead the D-class personnel to Task Force Tau-9's armory.

  The D-class and the remaining members arm themselves from the armory and break into SCP-2662's containment unit.



  Agents ████ and ██████, the 2 remaining available members of Task Force Tau-9, begin undressing the D-class personnel that are not guarding.

  SCP-2662 attempts to alert Task Force Tau-9 to no response.

  Agents ████ and ██████ begin carving symbols into the buttocks and thighs of the undressed D-class personnel. The D-class personnel begin to engage in group sex after being carved.



  All D-class personnel currently engaged in sex cease their movements. They all turn to stare at SCP-2662. Task Force Tau-9 arrive at the off-site meeting point only to be told no-such mission exists. Task Force Tau-9 begin moving back to Site ██.









 SCP-2662 moves to the shower stall and turns on the water. It sits in the shower stall for the remainder of the incident.
